<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Shipping & Delivery Policy | CodeCollab</title>
  <%- include('head-scripts') %>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: white;
    }

    .top-navbar {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      height: 60px;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    .navbar-brand {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .policy-container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .policy-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }

    .policy-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .last-updated {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .section {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #3b82f6;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .section p, .section li {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .section ul {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .section li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .back-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .back-link:hover {
      color: white;
    }

    .highlight-box {
      background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .highlight-box i {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #3b82f6;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .delivery-features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .delivery-feature {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .delivery-feature i {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #10b981;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .delivery-feature h4 {
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .delivery-feature p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Top Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg top-navbar">
    <div class="container-fluid px-4">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
        <i class="bi bi-code-slash me-2"></i>
        CodeCollab
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="policy-container">
    <a href="/" class="back-link">
      <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i>
      Back to Home
    </a>

    <div class="policy-card">
      <h1 class="policy-title">Shipping & Delivery Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: January 2, 2026</p>

      <div class="highlight-box">
        <i class="bi bi-cloud-check"></i>
        <h3 style="color: white; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">100% Digital Service</h3>
        <p style="margin: 0;">CodeCollab is a cloud-based software service. No physical products are shipped or delivered.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>1. Digital Service Delivery</h2>
        <p>CodeCollab Pro subscription is delivered instantly upon successful payment. Here's what you receive:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Immediate Access:</strong> Pro features are activated within seconds of payment confirmation</li>
          <li><strong>Email Confirmation:</strong> You'll receive a confirmation email with your subscription details</li>
          <li><strong>Dashboard Update:</strong> Your dashboard will reflect Pro status immediately</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>2. Delivery Timeline</h2>
        <div class="delivery-features">
          <div class="delivery-feature">
            <i class="bi bi-lightning-charge"></i>
            <h4>Instant Activation</h4>
            <p>Pro features available immediately</p>
          </div>
          <div class="delivery-feature">
            <i class="bi bi-envelope-check"></i>
            <h4>Email Receipt</h4>
            <p>Within 5 minutes</p>
          </div>
          <div class="delivery-feature">
            <i class="bi bi-globe"></i>
            <h4>Global Access</h4>
            <p>Available worldwide 24/7</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>3. Access Requirements</h2>
        <p>To access CodeCollab Pro features, you need:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>A stable internet connection</li>
          <li>A modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, or Edge)</li>
          <li>Your registered account credentials</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>4. Service Availability</h2>
        <p>CodeCollab is available:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>24/7 Access:</strong> Our service is available round the clock</li>
          <li><strong>Global Coverage:</strong> Accessible from anywhere in the world</li>
          <li><strong>99.9% Uptime:</strong> We strive for maximum availability</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Occasional maintenance windows may occur, and users will be notified in advance when possible.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>5. No Physical Shipping</h2>
        <p>Since CodeCollab is entirely digital:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>No shipping address is required</li>
          <li>No shipping charges apply</li>
          <li>No delivery delays or tracking needed</li>
          <li>No physical items to return</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>6. Delivery Issues</h2>
        <p>If you don't see Pro features after payment:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Wait 5 minutes and refresh your browser</li>
          <li>Log out and log back in</li>
          <li>Check your email for payment confirmation</li>
          <li>Contact support at <strong>codecollabbeta@gmail.com</strong></li>
        </ul>
        <p>We typically resolve delivery issues within 1-2 hours during business hours.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>For any delivery-related queries:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> codecollabbeta@gmail.com</p>
        <p><strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 24 hours</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
